<!Doctype html>
<html lang="en-US">

<head>
    <meta content="text/html; charset=utf-8" http-equiv="Content-Type" />
</head>

<body>
    <table width="60%" border="0" cellspacing="0" cellpadding="0" style="margin-left:auto;margin-right:auto;">
        <tr>
            <td style="text-align: center; color: black;">
                <img src="https://tattoo-rez-assets.s3.amazonaws.com/Primary+Mark.png" height="150">
                <h1 class="confirmation-header" style="margin-top: 0px;">New tattoo appointment requested!</h1>
                <img src="https://tattoo-rez-assets.s3.amazonaws.com/tattoo_inking2.png" height="400">
                <p style="text-align: left;">Hi
                    <%= reservation.artist.name %>,
                </p>
                <p>You have received another appointment request! Below is the information about your upcoming request:</p>
                <div style="text-align: left; margin-top: 20px; margin-bottom: 20px;">
                    <p>
                        Name:
                        <%= reservation.user.first_name %>
                    </p>
                    <p>
                        Email:
                        <%= reservation.user.email %>
                    </p>
                    <p>
                        Phone:
                        <%= reservation.user.phone %>
                    </p>
                    <p>
                        Tattoo placement:
                        <%= reservation.tattoo_placement %>
                    </p>
                    <p>
                        additional tattoo information:
                        <%= reservation.description %>
                    </p>
                     <p>
                        Coverup:
                        <%= reservation.cover_up %>
                    </p>
                    <p>
                        Date availability requested:
                        <%= reservation.appt_start %> to
                            <%= reservation.appt_end %>
                    </p>
                </div>
                <p>Please connect with your potential customer for additional questions and get something on the books! Reach out to us for any support questions regarding this request.</p>
                <p>The Mad Rabbit Team</p>
                <a href="mailto:booking@madrabbit.com" target="_blank" style="color: white; background: none; background-color: black; vertical-align: middle; padding: 10px 40px; text-decoration: none; border:  1px solid black; display: inline-block;">
                    NEED HELP?             
                </a>
            </td>
        </tr>
    </table>
</body>

</html>